@startuml
!include _style.puml
title TO-BE 00 · Persistence Kernel 컴포넌트
left to right direction
skinparam nodesep 60
skinparam ranksep 75

package "브라우저 UI" {
  component "App UI\nprogress · notes · settings" as App
  component "Atlas Parent Coordinator\nStudy + Global iframe\n세대 검증 · ACK · broadcast" as Atlas
  component "Backup / Restore\nJSON schema v3" as Backup

  App -[hidden]down-> Atlas
  Atlas -[hidden]down-> Backup
}

package "단일 Persistence 계층" {
  component "Normalized Adapter\ncapture · validate\nstatus projection" as Adapter
  component "Persistence Kernel\ncanonical ownership\ncheckpoint · mirror" as Kernel
  component "Outbox Worker\nstable operationId\nWeb Lock · lease" as Worker

  Adapter -down-> Kernel : validated payload
  Kernel -down-> Worker : outbox ready
}

package "브라우저 영속 저장" {
  database "IndexedDB\nworking snapshot\noutbox · meta · checkpoints" as IDB
  database "localStorage\ncompatibility mirror\ndirty marker" as LS

  IDB -[hidden]down-> LS
}

package "원격 저장" {
  cloud "Supabase RPC" as RPC
  database "PostgreSQL\nrevision CAS\nappend-only history\nnormalized projection" as DB

  RPC -down-> DB : transaction
}

App -right-> Adapter : data-change
Atlas -right-> Adapter : accepted Atlas + Bridge
Backup -right-> Kernel : restore candidate
Kernel -left-> Backup : canonical backup
Kernel -right-> IDB : snapshot + outbox\none transaction
Kernel -right-> LS : verified mirror
Worker -right-> IDB : claim / ack
Worker -right-> RPC : expectedRevision\nsame operationId

note bottom of IDB
  기준 원본은 working snapshot이다.
  pending import와 iframe localStorage는
  읽기 우선권을 갖지 않는다.
end note

caption UI writer는 명령만 제출하고, 기준 상태·재시도·복구 이력은 Persistence Kernel이 소유한다.
@enduml
